T02TD1288E:143b-1: he badzra ba lim ta bidhi n'a ma /
T02TD1288E:143b-3: kye'i rdo rje zhes bya ba'i gtor ma'i cho ga / kye'i rdo rje la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1288E:143b-4: nam mkha' kun du rgyu grub pa'i //
T02TD1288E:143b-6: de dang de yi bya ba ni //
T02TD1288E:143b-7: gtor ma'i cho ga cung zhig bshad //
T02TD1288E:143b-8: de la gtor ma rnams gsum ste //
T02TD1288E:143b-9: dkyil 'khor chen po'i lha rnams dang //
T02TD1288E:143b-10: de sprul mkha' 'gro ma rnams dang //
T02TD1288E:143b-11: mgron gyur phyogs skyong rnams la'o //
T02TD1288E:143b-12: dkyil 'khor chen po'i lha la ni //
T02TD1288E:143b-13: re zhig byin gyis brlab pa yang //
T02TD1288E:143b-14: bdag nyid 'dod pa'i lhar mos pas //
T02TD1288E:143b-15: snod dag mchog tu gyur pa ru //
T02TD1288E:143b-16: gtor ma'i rdzas ni bdud rtsir bsam //
T02TD1288E:143b-17: de bstan de nyid gsum sngags brjod //
T02TD1288E:143b-18: yang na 'dod yon lngar gyur par //
T02TD1288E:143b-19: bsam zhing byin gyis brlabs sngags brjod //
T02TD1288E:143b-20: de rjes mdun du dkyil 'khor ba'i //
T02TD1288E:143b-21: lha rnams skad cig rdor 'dzin bsam //
T02TD1288E:143b-22: de rnams dbul ba'i rim pa ni //
T02TD1288E:143b-23: aom ma h'a bh'u ta kh'a hi /
T02TD1288E:143b-24: grihna gri hna bhu nydza bhu nydza kha kha kh'a hi /
T02TD1288E:143b-25: ai dam bi lim ta kh'a hi /
T02TD1288E:143b-26: aa mri ta r'a sa kh'a hi /
T02TD1288E:143b-27: k'a ma gu ni sa m'a ra sa kh'a hi /
T02TD1288E:143b-28: zhes glu blangs so so'i mtshan dang sbyar ba ni /
T02TD1288E:143b-29: aom he badzra ne ra a'atm'a ta ai dam ma h'a ba lim ta kh'a hi /
T02TD1288E:143b-30: de bzhin du aom badzra goo r'i ai dam ma h'a ba lim ta kh'a hi /
T02TD1288E:143b-31: zhes bya ba la sogs pa brjod do //
T02TD1288E:143b-32: de ltar tshim zhing mnyes gyur nas //
T02TD1288E:143b-33: bdag nyid bsgrub pa rkyen sbyor pa'i //
T02TD1288E:143b-34: mkha' 'gro ma yi gtor ma ni //
T02TD1288E:143b-35: re zhig byin brlabs sngags dang mtshungs //
T02TD1288E:143b-36: dbul thabs bdag nyid 'dod lha yi //
T02TD1288E:143b-37: mdun du dam tshig rjes dran nas //
T02TD1288E:143b-38: mkha' 'gro ma rnams skad cig gis //
T02TD1288E:143b-39: tha snyad tshul du rab gyur nas //
T02TD1288E:143b-40: gtor ma'i longs spyod bya phyir dang //
T02TD1288E:143b-41: las dang sgrub la rab bskul la //
T02TD1288E:143b-42: de rnams dbul ba'i rim pa ni //
T02TD1288E:143b-43: lhag ma bsdus pa'i rim pa las //
T02TD1288E:143b-44: sngags 'di glu ru bcas pa brjod //
T02TD1288E:143b-45: aom au tsi shta ba lim ta badzra d'a ki n'i sam pa ni na /
T02TD1288E:143b-49: ai dam au tsishta ba lim ta kha kha kh'a hi /
T02TD1288E:144a-1: sidhi sam pa ni na sv'a h'a /
T02TD1288E:144a-2: de nas las dang dngos grub pa stsol //
T02TD1288E:144a-3: mngon par 'dod pa'i phrin las bcol //
T02TD1288E:144a-4: mgron gyur 'byung po'i gtor ma ni //
T02TD1288E:144a-5: mdun du chos 'byung gru gsum las //
T02TD1288E:144a-6: steng dang 'og dang bar dag tu //
T02TD1288E:144a-7: chu skyes 'dab brgyad rim bzhin bsam //
T02TD1288E:144a-8: steng dus bon aom gyur las //
T02TD1288E:144a-9: zla nyi nas gzung tshangs sogs par //
T02TD1288E:144a-10: mdog dkar rdo rje dril 'dzin pa //
T02TD1288E:144a-11: dbu la sku yi mtshan ma dag / rang 'dra'i tshogs pa brgyad du bsam //
T02TD1288E:144a-13: ma yi lhar gyur phyogs skyong brgyad //
T02TD1288E:144a-14: sa bon brgyad gyur mdog sngon po //
T02TD1288E:144a-16: dbu la thugs kyis mtshan par bsam //
T02TD1288E:144a-17: 'og tu klu brgyad sa las byung //
T02TD1288E:144a-18: mdog dmar rdo rje dril 'dzin zhing //
T02TD1288E:144a-19: dbu la gsung gi rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1288E:144a-20: rang 'dra dang ni ldan par bsgom //
T02TD1288E:144a-21: de nas re zhig byin brlabs pa //
T02TD1288E:144a-22: dam tshig bdud rtsi'i snod bcas pa //
T02TD1288E:144a-23: rlung dang me sogs smin byed pa //
T02TD1288E:144a-24: de rjes bdud rtsi dang sres la //
T02TD1288E:144a-25: gong du brjod pa'i lha rnams kyis //
T02TD1288E:144a-26: 'od zer spu gu lha rnams lces //
T02TD1288E:144a-27: longs spyod pas ni tshim par byed //
T02TD1288E:144a-28: de tshe ze'u 'bru rnam gsum la //
T02TD1288E:144a-29: tshangs dang 'dod lha sa yi lha //
T02TD1288E:144a-30: rim pa bzhin du bsam par bya //
T02TD1288E:144a-31: de yi sngags brjod bskul bcas pa //
T02TD1288E:144a-32: rdo rje dril bu gsil gsor bya //
T02TD1288E:144a-63: aom aa k'a ro mu kham sarbba dharm'a n'am a'a dya nutpanna tv'a ha'/
T02TD1288E:144a-64: aom a'a: h'um phat sv'a h'a /
T02TD1288E:144a-65: phan yon sngon du bsngo ba ni //
T02TD1288E:144a-66: res 'ga' gtor ma btang ba dang //
T02TD1288E:144a-67: rgyun du btang ba'i phan yon ni //
T02TD1288E:144a-68: rgyud du gsungs pa bzhin brjod do //
T02TD1288E:144a-69: bla ma dam pa'i rjes 'brang yid brtan zhing //
T02TD1288E:144a-70: 'phral la mngon du byed cing byin rlob pa //
T02TD1288E:144a-71: dam pa 'ga' yis gsol btab nas //
T02TD1288E:144a-72: man ngag gzhung bzhin mthun par bris pa yin //
T02TD1288E:144a-73: bcom ldan 'das kye'i rdo rje zhes bya ba'i gtor ma'i cho ga'i rim pa rdzogs so//
